          Greenland's abundant natural resources, from rare minerals to clean
          energy, hold tremendous economic development potential.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {
          naturalResources.map((resource) => (
            <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-liberation-blue transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-liberation-blue/20 group">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
                <span class="text-5xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                  {resource.icon}
                </span>
                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-liberation-blue px-3 py-1 bg-liberation-blue/10 rounded-full uppercase">
                  {resource.category}
                </span>
              </div>

              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-liberation-blue transition-colors">
                {resource.title}
              </h3>

              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                {resource.description}
              </p>

              <div class="border-t border-slate-700 pt-4 space-y-2">
                {resource.stats.map((stat) => (
                  <div class="flex items-center text-xs text-slate-500">
                    <svg
                      class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400 mr-2 flex-shrink-0"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
